      "raw_text": "Cyrus Happy has been chosen by\nthe local irrigation association to go\nto Olympia and urge the passage of\nan act by the legislature appropriate\ning $4,000 for surveys. Mr. Happy\nis to address an irrigation meeting\nin Wenatchee February 2.\n\n\nArrangements are progressing for\nan irrigation convention to be held\nin Spokane soon after March I."
